			</button>
		</div>
		<div class="ld-hero-actions ld-reveal ld-delay-2">
			<a href="/getting-started/quickstart" class="ld-btn ld-btn-primary">Get Started →</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/nullbrainlabs/dotai" class="ld-btn ld-btn-outline">GitHub</a>
		</div>
